Allows a person to log in for the purposes of OAuth, and returns the OAuth authentication cookie. For users signed up on the platform; other users log in using the <span class="apidoc_code"><a href="../oauth_login/m_oauth_login_ssoLoginPost.htm">POST&nbsp;/oauth/login/ssoLogin</a></span> operation.